Definition: a member of the branch of Islam that regards Ali as the legitimate successor to Mohammed and rejects the first three caliphs
Synonyms: Shi, ite, Shiite_Muslim, ite_Muslim, Shia_Muslim, Muslim, noun, group, Shiah, m, a, member, of, the, branch, Islam, that, regards, Ali, as, legitimate, successor, to, Mohammed, and, rejects, first, three, caliphs
Category: noun.person
